  "texts": [
    "In total, we acquired 60 reappraisals across 12 calls for our six vignettes.",
    "Generating ratings.",
    "Before providing ratings, participants completed the same reappraisal training as the participants in the reappraisal generation task.",
    "The only difference between the trainings was that the present participants were instructed to use their training to evaluate the quality EXPLORING HUMAN AND AI EMOTIONAL SUPPORT of others' reappraisals, as opposed to producing reappraisals.",
    "In each trial, participants viewed a vignette and a respective reappraisal, randomized from a pool of 671 reappraisals of the six vignettes."
  ],
